.SH "NAME"
vfs_full_audit \- record Samba VFS operations in the system log
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
.HP \w'\ 'u
vfs objects = full_audit
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
.PP
This VFS module is part of the
\fBsamba\fR(7)
suite\&.
.PP
